## 🏗️ Architecture: The Genius Loop

```mermaid
graph TD
    User([Command]) --> Retriever[Bi-Encoder Fast Retrieval]
    Retriever --> |Top 5| Reranker[Cross-Encoder Precise Rerank]
    Reranker --> |High Confidence| Execute[Agent Execution]
    Reranker --> |Low Confidence| Vision[Vision Watchdog / Screenshot]
    Vision --> RePlanner[ManagerAgent Re-plan]
    Execute --> |Error| RePlanner
    RePlanner --> Execute
    Execute --> Speak[Humanized Voice Response]
```

## 🧪 Verification Plan
 1. **Reranker Test**: "Tell me what's on my screen" -> Verify it scores `take_screenshot` higher than `brightness_up`.
 2. **Self-Correction**: "Open Claw" (App missing) -> Verify it falls back to Web Search for "Claw Mac app."
 3. **Sync Test**: Verify no "Didn't catch that" errors during startup briefings.
